The tools folder contains some useful tool for using processing.py on linux, with jedit and especially opengl on 64 bit linux.
The examples demonstrate the terse syntax of python (cf java and even regular processing in some instances), also some deficiencies/anomalies of python, lack of switch, lack of mutable string (alternative solutions are presented).